screen_desc: A screenshot of a ride reservation app interface. The top section features an illustration of a woman with a suitcase, standing in front of a car with a scenic background of palm trees and mountains. Below the illustration, the text "Reserve" is prominently displayed, followed by three features of the reservation service: "Choose your exact pickup time up to 90 days in advance," "Extra wait time included to meet your ride," and "Cancel at no charge up to 60 minutes in advance." At the bottom, there is a black button labeled "Reserve a ride."
